1.title: The Real Battle of LA/Queen Mary Menace

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

1.plot: In the season premiere, the team investigates the mysterious case that many people believe marked the very beginning of UFO government cover-ups -- the historic Battle of LA. Only a couple of months after Pearl Harbor, enemy aircraft was reported over Los Angeles, and the city erupted into a fiery battle that lasted for several hours. But no one knows what the military was actually shooting at, and the Fact or Faked team is determined to figure out if it was of extraterrestrial origin. Meanwhile, Bill, Chi-Lan and Austin spend the night on the haunted Queen Mary ...

2.title: Thermal Theater Ghost/Fire in the Sky

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

2.plot: Bill, Chi-Lan and Austin head to Jacksonville to investigate a video of a ghost sitting in the balcony of the haunted Florida Theater. Meanwhile, when a mysterious triangular formation of lights appears in the skies over both New York and Texas within a few days of each other, Ben, Jael and Devin head to El Paso to see what they can uncover.

3.title: Raining UFO's/Ectoplasmic Pic

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

3.plot: On this episode of Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files, the team takes on an unusual UFO case with video captured in flight by a police helicopter's night vision camera. Ben, Jael and Austin attempt to recreate a spherical ball of what appears to be liquid fire expelling white-hot droplets over the Long Beach Harbor. Bill, Chi-Lan and Devin try to crack a case in Winnipeg, Canada where a prominent surgeon from the 1920's took thousands of photographs that purport to illustrate the paranormal phenomenon known as Ectoplasm.

4.title: Playground Poltergeist/Alien Intruder

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

4.plot: On this episode of Fact or Faked, Austin, Bill and Jael fly to South America to investigate a mysterious case that has attracted worldwide attention and stumped both scientists and structural engineers. Meanwhile, Ben, Chi-Lan and Devin explore a bizarre alien abduction case in Milton, Florida.

5.title: Dashcam Chupacabra/Nightly News Alien

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

5.plot: On this episode of Fact or Faked, Ben, Chi-Lan and Devin travel to DeWitt County, Texas to investigate sightings of the mythical bloodsucker known as the Chupacabra. Austin, Bill and Jael are busy in Santa Cruz, Argentina where an alien has turned up in the news.

6.title: Whaley Ghost House/Muck Monster

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

6.plot: On this episode of Fact or Faked, Austin, Bill and Chi-Lan examine a series of mysterious photographs capturing ghostly images in one of the most haunted houses in America -- the historic Whaley House of San Diego, California. Meanwhile, Ben, Devin and Jael dive into a case that has baffled locals along the inter-coastal waterways of South Florida.

7.title: UFO Crash Landing/Graveyard Ghost

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

7.plot: In this episode, Ben, Jael and Devin venture deep into the deserts of New Mexico to investigate explosive footage of what many claim is a UFO crashing and disintegrating at the top secret White Sands missile testing facility.

8.title: Area 51/Cajun Apparition

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

8.plot: Bill, Lanisha and Devin journey to the Historic supposedly haunted Myrtles Plantation in Louisiana to investigate a video of what the witness described as an evil mist like entity.

9.title: Sinister Spirals/Flying Saucers

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

9.plot: Ben, Lanisha and Devin head to Santa Ana, California to investigate a classic flying saucer case that has divided the UFO community for years.

10.title: Asylum Apparition/Mystery Over Mexico

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

10.plot: Bill, Devin and Jael head south of the border to Guadalajara, Mexico to investigate the origins of a video that supposedly shows a fleet of traveling UFO'S; one of the largest UFO sightings ever captured.

11.title: Old West Haunting/Freeway Flyer

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

11.plot: Ben, Lanisha and Devin saddle up and head to Tombstone, Arizona to tackle a mysterious piece of footage from the historic Bird Cage Theater.

12.title: Bar Fright/Mexico City Cave Witch

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

12.plot: Bill, Lanisha and Devin pay a visit to a local watering hole in Humble, Texas where surveillance video of an exploding ashtray purports to validate the barÃ.s long-rumored history of poltergeist activity.

13.title: The Grim Sleeper/The Real Mr. Freeze

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

13.plot: Bill, Devin and Lanisha visit Atlanta to investigate the case of a woman who was terrorized by an unseen force during the night. Ben, Jael and Austin hit the deep freeze and welcome the world famous "Ice Man" to Los Angeles.

14.title: Bay Area Hysteria/Jersey Shore Haunting

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

14.plot: Ben, Austin and Jael investigate a mysterious hovering light over the waters of Bodega Bay, California. Bill, Lanisha and Devin travel to the Jersey Shore's Paramount Theater where amateur ghost hunters caught a humanoid apparition.

15.title: Vanishing Victim/Sky Serpent

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

15.plot: Ben, Jael and Devin head to Droitwich, England to investigate a piece of footage purportedly documenting an alien abduction.

16.title: Pride House Specter/Bluegrass Bigfoot

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

16.plot: Bill, Austin, and Devin travel to Jefferson, TX, to investigate a piece of truly haunting photographic evidence captured at the historic Pride House.

17.title: Battleship UFO

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

17.plot: Ben, Jael, and Devin head to the historic WWII battleship USS North Carolina to investigate photos and video of a strange apparition rumored to be the ghost of a dead sailor.

18.title: Reptile Rampage/Gasoline Ghoul

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

18.plot: Ben, Jael, and Austin journey to the swamps of Bishopville, South Carolina on the hunt for the terrifying Lizard Man.

19.title: Glowing Gargoyle/Phantom Feline

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

19.plot: Ben, Jael, and Devin head all the way to the United Kingdom to investigate a video of what looks like a hideous gargoyle with glowing eyes leaping through the darkness. And for this case, they enlist the help of Destination Truth's Josh Gates to hunt for the answers.

20.title: Florida Woodland UFO/Black Forest Entity

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

20.plot: Bill, Lanisha, and Devin journey to the swamps of Florida to investigate video of a golden shimmering UFO traveling silently through the air.

21.title: Graveyard Lightning/Truck Stop Terror

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

21.plot: Paranormal Files, Ben Jael, and Devin venture to Logtown, Mississippi on the trail of a mysterious glowing entity photographed by a paranormal investigator in the allegedly haunted Point Cemetery. The team cranks up the voltage on a series of experiments designed to replicate what looks like an otherworldly bolt of energy directed at a gravestone.

22.title: Into the Vortex/Tavern Shapeshifter

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

22.plot: Ben, Jael, and Austin head to the Pacific Northwest to investigate the Oregon Vortex, a famed mystery spot said to contain visual and perceptual paranormal phenomena.

23.title: Surveillance Specter/Morgue Mystery

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

23.plot: On this episode of Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files, Bill, Austin, and Jael venture across the pond to investigate a mysterious piece of surveillance video shot outside the historic Belgrave Hall in northern England. The team explores a few different theories to determine whether the alleged apparition caught on tape was something environmental or truly paranormal.

24.title: Iceland Worm Monster/Stonehenge Secrets

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

24.plot: In this episode of Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files, Ben, Jael, and Devin are joined on the road by Destination Truth's Josh Gates as they head to Iceland to investigate video appearing to show a large aquatic snake gliding through the icy waters of a volcanic river. With centuries of sightings in the region, the team has to employ some creative methods to explain this mysterious monster.

1.title: Burning Rubber/Hyperjump

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

1.plot: The Fact or Faked team investigates the mysterious case of a Georgia Ghost car caught of police tape passing through a wire fence and a series of unusual jumping lights at a UFO hot-spot near Phoenix, Arizona.

2.title: Unwanted Visitors/Strange Sightings

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

2.plot: In Fresno, the appearance of two creatures on a homeowner's CCTV screen has left him shaken and mystified. The team investigates the possibilities and what seems like a classic hoax only gets more puzzling. While in Lake Havasu, a vacationer's video camera catches a flying saucer floating above the lake and the attention of thousands on the Internet. Ben and the team perform a series of experiments in an attempt to explain the phenomenon.

3.title: Off the Deep End/Houseguest

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

3.plot: In Raystown, Pennsylvania a large lake is the scene for a series of sightings and a photo of what looks like Pennsylvania's very own Loch Ness Monster. The team suits up in diving gear to investigate the alleged creature. While in Los Angeles, two homeowners claim they have spent close to a decade communicating with the spirit world through the medium of photographs. Armed with the latest paranormal equipment, the team takes on the claim to see if it is fact or faked.

4.title: Predator/Red Sky at Night

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

4.plot: A mysterious video shows a large predator racing across the harsh terrain of Dartmoor in the United Kingdom. The investigation ends with a shocking discovery. While in El Cajon, California, the UFO community is in an uproar over a series of sightings involving a large triangular craft.

5.title: Blazing Horizon/Rollover

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

5.plot: For the past 50 years Paulding, Michigan has been at center of a controversy involving mysterious light on the horizon. Using everything from a high-powered laser to a light aircraft, the team investigates what has caused thousands of onlookers to ask, "What is that?" While in San Antonio, Texas a lonely railroad crossing serves as the backdrop for a 70-year debate where the road slopes up to the tracks, yet parked cars seem to roll uphill over the tracks.

6.title: The Caretaker/Cutter

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

6.plot: In Indiana, while investigating an abandoned cemetery a ghost hunter inadvertently captures what she believes is the ghost of Civil War soldier. The team uses everything at their disposal to try and eliminate the possibility of a hoax or even natural phenomenon. While in Colorado, a series of shocking cattle mutilations leave ranchers speculating that something from the sky abducts and experiments on their livestock. Using a series of scientific methods, the team determines whether there is a more natural explanation for the case.

7.title: Haunted Mansion Mist/Starlight Intruder

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

7.plot: After choosing two compelling cases to investigate, Ben, Austin and Chi-Lan travel to Alton, Illinois to test a mysterious cloud of mist that appears in a video taken inside the historic - and reportedly haunted - McPike Mansion. Bill, Jael and Larry take off to Northern California to investigate a strange UFO case in Fremont. They attempt to replicate the delta shaped light formation seen in the footage by launching a variety of illuminated objects into the sky and obtain surprising results.

8.title: Symphonic Spirits/Hovering Humanoid

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

8.plot: In a chilling new episode, Bill, Chi-Lan and Larry travel to Victor, New York to investigate the haunted Valentown Museum where a full-bodied ghost was purportedly caught on videotape. Meanwhile, Ben, Jael and Austin head to Texas to get to the bottom of a mysterious clip showing what appears to be a witch or flying humanoid soaring along a ridgeline.

9.title: Sasquatch Sprint/Alien Attacker

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

9.plot: After choosing two more intriguing cases to investigate, Bill, Austin and Chi Lan travel to Chopaka Lake, WA, to investigate a compelling video that many claim is solid proof of a Bigfoot in the remote area. Meanwhile in upstate Washington, Ben, Jael and Larry take on a case that has divided the paranormal community for over ten years - the staggering case of Dr Reed and the woodland Alien attack.

10.title: Mystery Mermaid/Ghostly Guardian

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

10.plot: In this week's episode of Fact or Faked, Ben, Jael and Austin travel to the land down under to investigate a mermaid case in Cairns, Australia. Meanwile, Bill, Chi-Lan and Larry travel to Mililani Hawaii, to visit a local family that believes they have captured photos of a guardian angel.

11.title: Lunar Landing Hoax/Tropical Intruder

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

11.plot: In this otherworldly episode of Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files, Ben, Austin and Chi-Lan set their sights on... the moon. Bill, Jael and Larry descend on the paranormal hotspot of Gulf Breeze, Florida to investigate a UFO case with footage that's never been seen before on television.

12.title: Bayou Beast/River Ghost

episode of.title: Fact or Faked: Paranormal Files (TV Series 2010– )

12.plot: In the final episode of the season, Ben, Larry and Chi-Lan travel down to the Louisiana Bayou in search of the legendary Honey Island Swamp Monster. Meanwhile, Bill, Austin and Jael head to Portland Oregon to investigate a strange light hovering over the haunted Willamette River.
